Cook pasta according to package directions. Toss vegetables with 1 tablespoon oil and 1 teaspoon Grill Mates(R) Montreal Chicken Seasoning. Place vegetables in a grill basket or on skewers; grill until tender, about 8-10 minutes, turning frequently. Combine balsamic vinegar, remaining oil and remaining Grill Mates(R) Montreal Chicken Seasoning in a large bowl. Add cooked pasta and vegetables and toss well. Serve warm or chilled.